message.body: Omg! I just realized I never text you back! I meant to on Wednesday but then I got caught up doing homework I guess. But I don't think I'll be going to that concert. Unforeseen circumstances caused me to have to give up more money, and I don't know if I like her too much. Some songs were decent, but I don't know if I'd like a whole concert of it.
Oh don't worry about it! It sold out anyways hahahah. Oh man, Is everything okay?
Oh no! So you don't get to go? I hope I didn't cause you to lose out! But yeah, just gmom.
No really don't worry about it! It wasn't meant to be. I probably shouldn't be spending money on concerts anyways hahah. Oh gotcha. You're a good granddaughter :)
What I wanted to say should not be said about another's grandmother. But I believe in karma.
I do too. And you've done a very generous, kind act which I believe you will be rewarded for. You've done your part!
Fat salmon with my sister tomorrow. We just made it. Thats about it.
I still haven't been there yet! Tam went and she said it's really expensive.
It is. But I love it!
Wait she sent to Pod! Hahahah. Man, now I want sushi.
